{
  "stem": "15694.12",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably the last.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyway, I joined a-- about a thousand youngsters all naked and practically all Muselmann on the way out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our clothes, our so-called pajama suits were taken away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whereas in previous camps I can't recall having had lice, but in this particular one, on the train, I had-- one of my main jobs was killing lice.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is by the by.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I took away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I never give it back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the middle was a door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it went in two parts-- probably 500 in each.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I calculated that because-- well, I'll tell you that in a minute.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But before that, I must have done something wrong because one man dressed-- took me back into the previous room and asked me to kneel on a-- I'm not sure what I have done wrong-- on a-- on a stool.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And before he sort of-- I want to make it a little bit shorter now and quicker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before long, I managed to run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wouldn't sort of find me amongst the others, anyway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went through a door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, having come late there, I had to join four others in a bed what is-- which is normally meant for one-- four.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were all crowded with fours and fives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And thought I was clever when I managed to be on the side where we, like sardines-- three on one side, two on the other-- was on the side where there was only one more.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when their legs all came on top of us, I don't-- I didn't think it was so clever anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the more on the other side, the more legs come on top of you.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
